/timeout: You can timeout a member by using /timeout.
/say: You can say anything to the bot, and the bot can echo back your message by using /say.
/ban: You can ban a member by using /ban.
/kick: You can kick a member by using /kick.
/give_role: You can give a member a role by using /give_role.
/avatar: You can get the avatar of a member by using /avatar.
/purge: You can purge messages by using /purge.
/feedback_setup: You can setup feedback channel by using /feedback_setup.
/feedback: You can send feedback to the bot by using /feedback.
